title: Rustic Ridge Classic Genuine Leather Journal - Handmade Leather Diary/Notebook/Sketchbook
features: Unique rustic leather journal with wrap tie closure by Rustic Ridge Leather.
Hand made with high quality genuine leather. Size: 5" x 7"
Includes 200 pages of handmade, cream colored, acid-free paper (100 sheets).
Perfect size to carry with you on trips, vacations, or daily journaling.
Blank pages work great for both writing and sketches.
description: This Classic Leather Journal by Rustic Ridge Leathergoods is the perfect way to record your adventures, thoughts, poetry, sketches, and more. The rustic leather cover is made from high quality leather that not only looks great, but will last for years to come.

The Classic Journal includes 200 cream colored pages (100 sheets) that are hand sewn into the leather binding. The acid-free, cotton rag pages are the perfect surface for writing or sketching with a pencil, ball point pen, or your favorite fountain pen.

The Rustic Ridge Classic Leather Journal gives a uniquely classic look, style, and feel that you will not find in a modern style journal or notebook. Natural variations in the leather make each journal a one of a kind, and adds to the character of each one. This journal makes an excellent gift for the writer or artist in your life, or you can buy it for yourself. Either way, you will be pleasantly surprised with the look, smell, and quality of this hand made leather journal by Rustic Ridge.
